<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/bob_m_fw/">www.geocities.com/bob_m_fw/</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Here's what these mods will do:<br>
<br>
-Remove the Spellbook and Pet Info buttons from Window Selector<br>
-Remove the Pet Info window altogether (Since we don't get pets)<br>
-Removes the titles from many windows, including CHAT. (No more mis-clicking the top of your chat window when trying to loot)<br>
-Adds your Primary and Secondary melee slots to the TOP of all of your bags (for easy weapon switching)<br>
-Makes the Hotboxes horizontal to save space and adds your leg slot and first bag in addition to the 10 boxes.<br>
-Adds alot of info including your WEIGHT, AC/ATK and AA Exp in the player screen.<br>
-Makes your Inventory look alot like the old-style one. Your class animation is where you drop things to auto-equip them.<br>
-Makes your buff window transparent and borderless as well as giving you the full buff names.<br>
-Health percentages are given for yourself, target, and group members.<br>
-Makes your confirmation boxes smaller. The normal ones with this UI used much more space than needed.<br>
-Removes the casting window and places a casting bar in your Player Window below your health instead. (only appears when you're using a clicky item with cast time)<br>
<br>
